name: //Fanzine// Darkwave Dream
description:
This is a digital fanzine I did inspired in 10 songs of the darkwave/postpunk musical genre that I like, all the art belongs to the beautiful Grunge Dreams series. 
//Imagining a life where some people had a place to call home and friends who become family under the spells of songs and poetry of the darkness and gloom. IA mother self-destructed//
